deo)"}, {"format_id": "dash-865463533190374v", "ext": "mp4", "width": 1080, "height": 1920, "tbr": 1303.334, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "vp09.00.40.08.00.01.01.01.00", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQMPnl7C6ycjEjJGTuUbPymZIeZSVLPa_dNTjjmboIYTVv7_821YBR-iKOsCopmNPYB3jHyExhKHVVH6OQudaVnHBYfYCvu14pDsCUY.mp4?_nc_cat=105&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=pfupJvGIPRMQ7kNvwFG3qYm&&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=tOl8WRxkOxnpJVMjzkU6Pg&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a32e&oh=00_Af0gqkPUsVeBYbekVFsCY15fPYZmS8nF6HD_qhzMV-nFfw&oe=69D7A0B2", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 14314843, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/91.0.4472.77 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1303.334, "format": "dash-865463533190374v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by sheinspiration___", "description": "Most parents would NEVER knowingly give their kids something that harms them…\n\nBut what if the things we were taught are “normal”…\nare actually the problem?\n\nThe same system that normalized sugary breakfast cereals for kids\nwas built on marketing, not health.\n\nBright boxes. Cartoon characters. “Part of a balanced breakfast.”\n\nMeanwhile…\nwe’re seeing more kids struggle with energy crashes, focus issues, weight gain, and blood sugar problems earlier than ever.\n\nThis isn’t about guilt — it’s about awareness.\n\nBecause once you SEE it, you can’t unsee it.\n\nI had to unlearn a lot too.\nAnd when I did, everything changed — not just for me, but for my kids and my whole family.\n\nWe didn’t need perfection…\nwe just needed a better approach to protect ourselves from what’s out there.\n\nCurious what you think about this 👇\nAre cereals something you still keep in your home?\n\nIf you want to learn the natural approach we use daily to support our health in today’s food environment, comment PROTOCOL and I’ll reach out 💬", "duration": 87.866, "timestamp": 1774633810, "uploader_id": "47844961066", "uploader": "Sheina", "channel": "sheinspiration___", "like_count": 122287, "comment_count": 3422, "comments": [{"author": "twintwinkg", "author_id": "2199007988", "id": "18577707451061489", "text": "@foodpharmer", "timestamp": 1775353434}, {"author": "benikosinclair", "author_id": "3474528256", "id": "18203142301339822", "text": "well I'll be.😳 what have I been eating all these years 😭", "timestamp": 1775352749}, {"author": "lyfe_with_bubbles", "author_id": "47536551404", "id": "18092419025130036", "text": "@kelloggsus what in the hell 😳 I have two boxes left I’m done with cereal", "timestamp": 1775352406}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/658352163_1622091212451939_626577767970403697_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gG65eFnLDrJolpd_GLNJScq7MZ1XE-aliHmWq86dOihEJgJoOUESOjYyx2fLR4sHvg&_nc_ohc=l0_siUXsfUMQ7kNvwEoz3QF&_nc_gid=tOl8WRxkOxnpJVMjzkU6Pg&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af1ytsTHrZd015MgqTwISRZpOKEqPaQ1fdMcJlA2_i2h_A&oe=69D7A62E&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/658352163_1622091212451939_626577767970403697_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gG65eFnLDrJolpd_GL